Package it.polimi.se2019.limperio.nicotera.italia.events.events_by_client

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerInitializationEvent
    Event to reply to the server after have received some RequestInitializationEvent.
    ClientEvent
    Event generated by some components located in client side.
    DiscardPowerUpCardToSpawnEvent
    Event generated bt the player when he decides a powerUp card to discard to be generated in the first turn or after a death.
    DrawTwoPowerUpCards
    Event to express the wish to draw two powerUp cards in the first turn.
    InvolvedPlayer
    Structure that store a player and square involved in an action like shoot or use of some powerUp cards
    RequestToCatchByPlayer
    Event to show to the controller the wish to do a catch action.
    RequestToRunByPlayer
    Event to show to the controller the wish to do a run action.
    RequestToShootByPlayer
    Event to show to the controller the wish to do a shoot action.
